## PART 6 — DATA MODEL FOR MERGED VERSIONS

```kotlin
// Represents one entry from the merged manifest
// (either from remote GitHub manifest or wine_proton_versions.json)
data class MergedVersionEntry(
    val id: String,             // unique id, e.g. "proton-8.0-arm64ec"
    val displayName: String,    // shown in UI, e.g. "Proton 8.0 (arm64ec)"
    val sourceGroup: String,    // "Proton-GE", "Wine", "Proton (Valve)", etc.
    val downloadUrl: String,
    val sizeMb: Float,
    val isInstalled: Boolean,
    val isLatest: Boolean,
    val isRecommended: Boolean
)
// ManifestRepository.getMergedVersionList(appId) returns List<MergedVersionEntry>
// It reads from the merged manifest (remote + wine_proton_versions.json assets)
// and marks isInstalled by checking Room / installed paths.
// It marks isRecommended by calling GameConfigRecommender.recommendedProtonVersion(hardware).
```

