## DESIGN CONSTRAINTS

- All chips: `Modifier.weight(1f).height(44.dp)` — equal width, fixed height, text never wraps
- "Uncapped" → "Off" to fit in one chip cell. If product requires "Uncapped", use `widthIn(min=64.dp)` instead of `weight(1f)` for that chip only
- Section labels: gnTextTertiary, 11sp, uppercase, bold, letterSpacing 0.08sp
- Field labels: gnTextPrimary, bodyMedium, medium weight, directly above chip row
- Toggle rows: bodyMedium label left, Switch right, gnAccentPrimary checked track
- Version picker row: gnBgElevated background, rounded 10dp, chevron right icon
- Version picker sheet: ModalBottomSheet over the settings sheet (z-order handled by Compose)
- Save button: weight(2f) so it is visually twice as wide as Cancel — makes it the primary action
- Cancel: outlined gnBorderCard — secondary, low prominence
- No new colors — only existing gn_* tokens
- Fonts: GameNativeFontFamily (Outfit) via PluviaTypography everywhere
- downloadVersion in ViewModel triggers ManifestInstaller's existing install flow
  (launchManifestContentInstall) — do not write a new download path
- After any Turnip/Mesa/Proton install completes, call HardwareProfileCache.invalidate(context)
